gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 116, Grizzlies 109
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeated the Grizzlies, 116-109. Devin Booker led the Suns with 34 points, 10 rebounds, and seven assists as Kevin Durant added 27 points (10-14 FG) and five assists. Jaren Jackson Jr. led the Grizzlies with a season-high 37 points and nine rebounds as Desmond Bane totaled 27 points, three rebounds, and five assists. The Suns improve to 12-8 as the Grizzlies fall to 5-14.
